sources.title: Tender Flesh, Carne Fresca 1997 Monique Parent, Amber Newman, Lina Romay, Aldo Sambrell, Analia Ivars, Mikel Kronen + Jess Franco
sources.description: Jess Franco's take on The Most Dangerous Game theme. Lots of standard Franco stuff here, night club act, special effects lens, though not as many zoom shots or close ups of Romay's genitals. Not the best resolution which is disappointing as it seems to have been shot on 35mm with good film stock.
